short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Track the price history of products on Etsy for the past 3 or 6 months

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Main features:
1. Price history chart, display price history within 3/6 months.
2. Search by image on AliPrice to find similar products on Aliexpress, eBay, Taobao, etc.
